a.不近人情的 【英】 adj.不近人情的(crue l, brutal, unkind etc.) adj. 不人道的 = brutal; 没有同情或怜悯的 【记】humane(adj 仁慈的) 【记】in非 + humane人→非人的 inhumane (adj.)  late 15c., from Latin inhumanus (see inhuman). Originally a variant spelling and pronunciation of inhuman, it appears to have died out 17c. but been revived c.1822 as a negative form of humane.
